The,service,provides,online,tools,for,business,organizations,to,manage,travel,and,expense,reporting,and,reimbursement,Integrated,travel,booking,functions,combine,with,expense,reporting,within,a,single,platform,The,API,allows,integration,with,applications,of,customer,companies,partner,service,providers,or,independent,third,party,developers,including,mobile,app,developers,API,methods,support,submission,and,tracking,of,travel,requests,and,booking,of,transportation,and,lodging,either,for,individuals,or,for,groups,completing,the,same,travel,Methods,also,support,creating,updating,and,submitting,expense,reports,as,part,of,a,reimbursement,process